("106","24","8","Which of the following statements comes close to describing what self-esteem is?","radio","Self esteem is when you show confidence and are not afraid~The core perceptions and beliefs that others have placed on us~The value or worth you unconsciously assign to yourselves\n\n","The value or worth you unconsciously assign to yourselves","","0"),
