("125","28","6","Situation 1: Njoki was invited to go with her friends to a birthday party. Everything was fine until some three boys came in with a bag full of bottles. It was as though everyone was waiting for this moment.\n\nThere was a lot of excitement in the room and everyone wanted to have the drinks. Njoki realized that it was beer and was shocked that some of her close friends were going for it. She knew it was wrong to do this. How would you help her say â€œNOâ€ assertively?","inputtext","","","","0"),
